 Most of the default penguin images were taken from the Pingus game. Alternative themes can be selected like this:

 The xpenguins package includes the themes Penguins, Big Penguins, Classic Penguins, Turtles and Bill. The xpenguins_themes package contains the extra themes The Simpsons, Sonic the Hedgehog, Lemmings and Winnie the Pooh (distributed separately because the license/copyright situation is unclear).

